cat << EOF
Murrine is a GTK+-2 theme engine. "Murrine" is an Italian word
meaning the glass artworks done by Venician glass blowers. The engine
is cairo-based, and it's very fast compared to clearlooks-cairo and
ubuntulooks.
EOF
